room_title: Escape room "The Missing Detective's Office" by Escape Room Downtown in Canton
room_description: Detective Swope went missing not too long after being hired by a mysterious Mrs. Anderson to find her brother who is on the run and hiding out somewhere in Canton. But cases can have their twists as Charlie soon found out after looking for him. Can you and your team of detectives follow the clues, work the puzzles left behind by Charlie, and solve the case in order to escape the room before 45 minutes expires?
